 INSTALLATION
 -------------

 1) Create a database
 2) Edit config.php and enter database parameters
 3) Run bmon ... -O db:<database parameters>
    Example: bmon -o null -O 'db:driver=mysql;password=XXX'
 4) Make this directory available on a PHP capable webserver

 NOTE: bmon will create the required tables itself, an empty
       database will suit you just fine.
